            <strong>Automation-ready web development</strong> combines modern development practices with intelligent automation tools to create websites and applications that can self-optimize, integrate seamlessly with business systems, and adapt to changing requirements without extensive manual intervention.
          </p>
          
          <!-- Market Growth Callout -->
