            <span class="text-2xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary">$25.5B</span>
            <span class="text-white ml-2">DevOps market projection by 2028 (19.7% CAGR)</span>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs mt-1">Source: Spacelift DevOps Statistics 2025</p>
          </div>
          
