            <span class="text-2xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary">&lt;1 day</span>
            <span class="text-white ml-2">service restoration time for leading DevOps performers</span>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs mt-1">Source: CD Foundation State of CI/CD Report 2024</p>
          </div>
          
          <p>
            This methodology leverages modern DevOps practices to achieve superior performance outcomes. <span class="text-primary font-bold">Leading DevOps performers restore service in less than one day</span> and maintain <span class="text-primary font-bold">change failure rates below 15%</span>, according to the CD Foundation's 2024 research.
          </p>
