                  <li>Scheduled, monolithic deployments</li>
                  <li>Manual server provisioning</li>
                  <li>Reactive security patching</li>
                  <li>Siloed teams (Dev, QA, Ops)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class=" p-3 rounded">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-primary mb-2">Automation-Ready Workflow</h4>
