            </div>
          </div>
          <p>
            Adopting an automation-ready approach yields transformative benefits, directly impacting a company's top and bottom lines. Organizations consistently report achieving the measurable improvements across speed, performance, cost, and architectural resilience.
          </p>
          
          <!-- DevOps Benefits Highlight -->
          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6 py-4 my-6 bg-primary/5 rounded-r-lg">
            <p class="text-lg text-white italic">"Leading DevOps performers achieve faster recovery times and lower change failure rates, with 99% of organizations reporting positive effects from DevOps implementation"</p>
            <cite class="text-primary text-sm">— CD Foundation State of CI/CD Report 2024 & Spacelift DevOps Statistics 2025</cite>
          </blockquote>
